  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment completed; all assessed factors reported as meeting or exceeding required credibility levels. The overall assurance level is declared Medium, consistent with MRL 2 expectations and the breadth of validation evidence assembled across five flow-speed operating points.",
